headline: BrightStar Credit Union Fuels Future Growth and Expansion with Jack Henry
summary: Jack Henry™ (Nasdaq: JKHY) announced that BrightStar Credit Union (BSCU) chose Jack Henry's Symitar® platform and complementary products to support its growth and deliver better member experiences.
